KingOfTheHill plugin for Bukkit

Dependencies:
 Factions
 Essentials

Commands:
 /koth init
   Initializes the KoTH faction. Must be used prior to any other commands.

 /koth gen
   Forces a hill reset

 /koth add
   Adds the current location as a hill location

 /koth remove
   Removes all hill locations in the current chunk

 /koth clear
   Clears all hill locations

